title: Modern problems 1981 chevy chase( mrithul.rs)
description:
this is one of the chevy chase's early film, and according to me,its not as intresting as his other movies..,but if u r a chevy chase fan, its still watchable





Chevy Chase is an air traffic controller having problems. He is having little success winning back his girlfriend until nuclear waste spills on his car giving him telekentic powers. The once meek, but now suddenly "empowered" Chase begins to wreak havoc on those who have annoyed him culminating in a weekend getaway at his friend's beach house where Chase's powers go out of control
